b'Safety Tips'
b'UIC Police offer the following security tips:'
b'Be aware of your surroundings'
b'Try to travel in groups when possible, particularly after dark'
b'Use well-lit walkways'
b'On campus, look for the location of the nearest emergency call box (there are more than 1,500 across campus)'
b'The emergency number for UIC Police is 5-5555 or 312-355-5555, which should be set on speed-dial on your cell phone'
b'Report crime promptly to police'
